# This file keeps the models/archive/ directory tracked by Git.
# It serves as the archive slot for retired champions in the lifecycle.
#
# Archived champions are written here automatically by scripts/promote.py
# under timestamped sub-directories, e.g.:
#   models/archive/champion_v2.0.0_20260321_120000/
#
# Each archive slot contains the full set of champion artifacts at the moment
# of the promotion that displaced it:
#   two_stage_pipeline.pkl
#   model_info.json
#   metrics.json
